                    color: FlutterFlowTheme.of(context).alternate,
                    width: 1,
                  ),
                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                ),
              ),
            ),
          ),
          Padding(
            padding: EdgeInsetsDirectional.fromSTEB(20, 0, 20, 12),
            child: AuthUserStreamWidget(
              builder: (context) => TextFormField(
